<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>FlowCRM | Calculadora de ROI para Automação de Marketing</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", "Manrope", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #191923;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* =========================
       HERO
    ========================= */

    .hero-section {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100svh;
      padding: 28px 24px 108px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 96% 6%, rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.18), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 82% 72%, rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.14), transparent 35%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 8% 22%, rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.07), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fff8f4 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-nav {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto clamp(56px, 7vw, 88px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      line-height: 1;
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, opacity 0.22s ease;
    }

    .logo:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .logo-image {
      width: 156px;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4f8b 0%, #ff7a30 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.24);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition:
        transform 0.22s ease,
        box-shadow 0.22s ease,
        filter 0.22s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.34);
      filter: saturate(1.04);
    }

    .button:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.26);
      outline-offset: 4px;
    }

    .button svg {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      transition: transform 0.22s ease;
    }

    .button:hover svg {
      transform: translateX(3px);
    }

    .nav-button {
      min-height: 46px;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.22);
    }

    .primary-button {
      min-height: 56px;
      padding: 19px 30px;
    }

    .hero-container {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.08fr) minmax(360px, 0.92fr);
      gap: clamp(44px, 6vw, 68px);
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 650px;
    }

    .hero-copy h1 {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 660px;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.55rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.075em;
      color: #191923;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      margin: 24px 0 0;
      max-width: 570px;
      font-size: clamp(1.04rem, 1.7vw, 1.18rem);
      line-height: 1.72;
      color: #4b4b5c;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      margin-top: 32px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .hero-microcopy {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      max-width: 450px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.13);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(25, 25, 35, 0.06);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-weight: 650;
      color: #5d5d6e;
    }

    .hero-microcopy::before {
      content: "";
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      margin-top: 1px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at center, #ff4f8b 0 2px, transparent 2.5px),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.16), rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.14));
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.18);
    }

    .hero-bullets {
      margin: 34px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px 18px;
      color: #30303d;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-bullets li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      min-height: 56px;
      padding: 14px 15px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.11);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(25, 25, 35, 0.055);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .bullet-icon {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.13), rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.13));
      color: #ff4f8b;
    }

    .bullet-icon svg {
      width: 17px;
      height: 17px;
      stroke: currentColor;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      justify-self: end;
    }

    .hero-visual::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 8% 2% auto 10%;
      width: 82%;
      height: 84%;
      border-radius: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.16), rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.12));
      filter: blur(14px);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-visual::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      right: -22px;
      bottom: -28px;
      width: 112px;
      height: 112px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.46);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.07);
      transform: rotate(12deg);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .mockup-frame {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 56px rgba(25, 25, 35, 0.14);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .mockup-frame img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 38px rgba(25, 25, 35, 0.09);
    }

    /* =========================
       CONTEXTO
    ========================= */

    .context-section {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 96px 24px;
      background: #fffaf7;
    }

    .context-container {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 72px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .section-label {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #ff4f8b;
    }

    .context-title h2 {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 520px;
      font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 4vw, 4.3rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: #191923;
    }

    .context-copy {
      max-width: 580px;
      padding-top: 44px;
    }

    .context-copy p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #4b4b5c;
    }

    .context-copy p + p {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    /* =========================
       RESPONSIVO
    ========================= */

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-section {
        min-height: auto;
        padding-bottom: 78px;
      }

      .hero-nav {
        margin-bottom: 56px;
      }

      .hero-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 58px;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .hero-copy h1,
      .hero-copy p {
        max-width: 720px;
      }

      .hero-visual {
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        justify-self: center;
      }

      .context-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 32px;
      }

      .context-copy {
        max-width: 100%;
        padding-top: 0;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .hero-bullets {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero-section {
        padding: 22px 20px 66px;
      }

      .hero-nav {
        margin-bottom: 48px;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .logo-image {
        width: 128px;
      }

      .nav-button {
        min-height: 42px;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .nav-button svg {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-copy h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.55rem, 14vw, 4rem);
        letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      }

      .hero-copy p {
        margin-top: 22px;
        font-size: 1.03rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .primary-button {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 54px;
        padding: 17px 22px;
      }

      .hero-bullets {
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      .hero-bullets li {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .hero-visual::after {
        display: none;
      }

      .mockup-frame {
        padding: 9px;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .mockup-frame img {
        border-radius: 18px;
      }

      .context-section {
        padding: 72px 20px;
      }

      .context-title h2 {
        max-width: 100%;
        font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 10vw, 3.2rem);
      }

      .context-copy p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 430px) {
      .hero-nav {
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .nav-button {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="hero-section">
    <nav class="hero-nav">
      <a href="#" class="logo" aria-label="FlowCRM">
        <img
          class="logo-image"
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/wk2nvqhl/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/logo_oficial_k6kpzn"
          alt="FlowCRM"
        >
      </a>

      <a href="#calculator" class="button nav-button">
        Acessar calculadora
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14m-6-6 6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <h1>Calcule o ROI da automação de marketing em menos de 2 minutos</h1>

        <p>
          Descubra quanto tempo sua equipe pode economizar ao automatizar tarefas
          manuais, melhorar fluxos de campanha e reduzir esforço operacional.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#calculator" class="button primary-button">
            Ver minha estimativa de economia
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M5 12h14m-6-6 6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <span class="hero-microcopy">
            Resultado estimado com base na rotina atual da sua equipe.
          </span>
        </div>

        <ul class="hero-bullets">
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M4 19V5m0 14h16M8 16v-5m4 5V8m4 8v-3" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Estime ganhos de produtividade</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <rect x="5" y="4.5" width="14" height="15" rx="2.5" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M9 9h6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M9 13h6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M9 17h4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <circle cx="7.2" cy="9" r="0.9" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
                <circle cx="7.2" cy="13" r="0.9" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
                <circle cx="7.2" cy="17" r="0.9" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Identifique tarefas que podem ser automatizadas</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8.2" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M12 7.2v9.6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M15.1 9.1h-4.2a1.9 1.9 0 0 0 0 3.8h2.2a1.9 1.9 0 0 1 0 3.8H8.8" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Visualize economia de tempo e recursos</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M12 3 4 7v6c0 5 3.5 7.5 8 8 4.5-.5 8-3 8-8V7l-8-4Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Receba recomendações para otimizar sua operação</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="mockup-frame">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/wk2nvqhl/image/upload/v1783472860/Mockup_de_painel_de_marketing_FlowCRM_nouecr.png" alt="Mockup da calculadora de ROI da FlowCRM">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="context-section">
    <div class="context-container">
      <div class="context-title">
        <span class="section-label">O desafio</span>
        <h2>Quanto tempo sua equipe ainda perde com tarefas manuais?</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="context-copy">
        <p>
          Campanhas, listas, aprovações, relatórios, follow-ups e ajustes operacionais
          fazem parte da rotina de marketing. O problema começa quando essas tarefas
          passam a consumir tempo demais e reduzem o espaço para análise, planejamento
          e melhoria contínua.
        </p>

        <p>
          Com processos mais bem estruturados e automações nos pontos certos, a equipe
          reduz retrabalho, ganha previsibilidade e mantém as campanhas rodando com
          mais consistência.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
